snippet: Arjen Robben has delayed signing a contract extension with Bayern Munich and says there are other clubs interested in him.
abstract: Bayern Munich winger Arjen Robben delays signing a contract extension, saying there are other soccer clubs interested in him; development comes in the wake of confrontation with Bayern teammate Franck Ribery.
lead_paragraph: Arjen Robben has delayed signing a contract extension with Bayern Munich and says there are other clubs interested in him.

headline.seo: Robben Delays New Deal with Bayern Munich
